name: Deutsche Digital Assets
public_notice: Iconic ICNQ (ICNQ) has rebranded to Deutsche Digital Assets (ICNQ). For more information, please view their website.

description.en: The ICNQ token powers the DDA ecosystem as both a voucher token and club membership instrument for Deutsche Digital Assets and its subsidiaries.
